videos.description: Dwayne Haskins finds Parris Campbell as the Buckeyes get on the board first.
videos.headline: Haskins finds Campbell for TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins drops a dime to Terry McLaurin for a 32-yard gain for the Buckeyes at the end of the first quarter.
videos.headline: Haskins finds McLaurin for 32-yard gain

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws to Johnnie Dixon, who's wide-open in the end zone, to put Ohio State up by two possessions.
videos.headline: Haskins hits Dixon for wide-open TD

videos.description: When a balloon is caught floating during the Rose Bowl, the referee snatches it out of mid-air and pops it.
videos.headline: Ref makes grab of balloon, pops it

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws a perfect pass to Rashod Berry at the end of the first half, Haskins' 50th touchdown pass of the season.
videos.headline: Haskins throws 50th TD pass of season

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws for three touchdowns to help Ohio State dominate the first half and lead Washington 21-3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ohio State up big on Washington at halftime of Rose Bowl) 2019/01/01 ESHEET Sotfull

videos.headline: Ohio State up big on Washington at halftime of Rose Bowl

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws a big 34-yard pass to K.J. Hill that sets up a J.K. Dobbins touchdown in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Haskins finds Hill to set up Ohio State TD

videos.description: Myles Gaskin pulls off his best Tim Tebow with a jump pass as Washington gets their first touchdown of the day.
videos.headline: Gaskin mimics Tebow with jump pass

videos.description: Washington scores off of a 1-yard Myles Gaskin run as the Huskies get the score to 28-17 in the fourth.
videos.headline: Gaskin scores to pull Washington closer to Ohio State

videos.description: Hunter Bryant pulls off a wild one-handed catch in the fourth quarter as he practically palms the football while coming down with it.
videos.headline: Bryant pulls off incredible one-handed catch

videos.description: Myles Gaskin reaches for the pylon and gets it by a hair to pull Washington to within 5 of Ohio State.
videos.headline: Gaskin pulls off wild dive for TD

videos.description: Urban Meyer reflects on his career and his team after Ohio State defeats Washington in the Rose Bowl 28-23.
videos.headline: Meyer: 'I'm a very blessed person'

videos.description: Urban Meyer reflects on his career with Rece Davis after hoisting the Rose Bowl Game trophy.
videos.headline: Meyer: 'I'm so proud of our players'

videos.description: Urban Meyer finishes his coaching career with a win at the Rose Bowl as Dwayne Haskins throws for 251 yards and three touchdowns.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Meyer wins Rose Bowl in farewell with Buckeyes) 2019/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Meyer wins Rose Bowl in farewell with Buckeyes

videos.description: Ohio State quarterback Dwayne Haskins reflects on the Buckeyes and his season with Maria Taylor after defeating Washington in the Rose Bowl.

videos.headline: Haskins on future: 'I haven't made a decision yet'

videos.headline: Meyer gets Gatorade bath after winning Rose Bowl

videos.description: During his final postgame speech as head coach, Urban Meyer hands his whistle to Ryan Day, who will become the 25th head coach of the Buckeyes.
